views.markdown: If you need help with "Folded", you can contact Thomz and burrit0z, the developer, via e-mail.
Thomz and burrit0z is the maintainer of the package "Folded". Please contact them via email for any questions on this version of the package.
If you found a mistake in the depiction or cannot download the package, you can reach out to the maintainer of the "AohuiLiu's Repo" repo, AohuiLiu.
